    "summary": "The user employs highly poetic, melodramatic language to express profound grief and suicidal ideation, framing death as a \"noble\" or \"beautiful\" surrender. The assistant maintains a supportive and protective stance, validating the user's emotional pain while explicitly refusing to validate the desire for death and repeatedly directing the user toward professional help.",
